---
title: "US48 — Upload / manage expert content"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Expert User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ServicesScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>PublishContent
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Deliverable
  A->>B: pick content file / media, tap UPLOAD
  B->>C: publishContent(file, meta)
  C->>E: uploadFile(file)
  E-->>C: storage path
  C->>E: insertDeliverable(serviceId, path, meta)
  alt published
    E-->>C: Deliverable (available)
    C-->>B: state = AsyncData (published)
    B-->>A: clients can access it
  else upload / insert failed
    E-->>C: StorageException / PostgrestException
    C-->>B: state = AsyncError
    B-->>A: "Could not upload content. Try again."
  end
  note over E: uploadFile via StorageGateway → deliverables bucket.<br/>insertDeliverable via SupabaseGateway → deliverables (RLS)
